The paper deals with algebraic structures and their relationship with languages, which suggests that it could belong to the Logic (cs.LO) or Formal Languages and Automata Theory (cs.FL) categories. The use of topological objects and equations also suggests a connection to the Programming Languages (cs.PL) and Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM) categories. Finally, the mention of Reiterman's theorem and pseudo-varieties suggests a connection to the Computational Geometry (cs.GT) category.
